data.description: Calling all Investors!! Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to invest in the revitalization and redevelopment of the Summerhill community.  This large corner lot features 2 properties and a 1 car garage.  Property Sold AS IS.  Bring your imagination and ideas to this property.  A prime location, just 1 block from Central Parc Stadium (formerly Braves Turner Field) and within minutes of the Atlanta Zoo, Atlanta Beltline, Georgia State Capitol and Georgia State University.  Lots of dining, shopping, arts and entertainment within walking distance.  Easy access to transit and major highways.
